downloadTitle: Microsoft Host Integration Server 2016 Software Development Kit
detailsSection: The Host Integration Server 2016 SDK provides headers, libraries and code samples which developers can use to create applications that utilize features of Host Integration Server 2016.
systemRequirementsSection:
This release is supported on the following operating systems:
  • Windows 10
  • Windows 8.1
  • Windows Server 2016
  • Windows Server 2012 R2
  • Virtualization with Azure and Hyper-V
The resources in this SDK can be used with any of the following versions of Visual Studio:
  • Visual Studio 2013
  • Visual Studio 2015
installInstructionSection:
1. Click the Download button on this page to start the download.
  2. Do one of the following:
  • To start the installation immediately, click Run.
  • To save the download to your computer for installation at a later time, click Save.
  • To cancel the download, click Cancel.
